metadata.name: 999 Balloons
metadata.description: 999 Balloons is an NFT project that was born to inspire hope and create an impact for our Ukrainian brothers and sisters. Help us in our stand for democracy over tyranny by donating today. 100% of the proceeds of this project will go directly to the Ukrainian people to support them in their resistance. There is no supply cap and you can donate as much as you want when minting your NFT. Donation floor is .01 ETH. Please donate what you can.
